headline: Eastman Chemical (EMN): Valuation Insights Following Leadership Changes, Insider Buying, and Dividend Growth
summary: Eastman Chemical (EMN) recently announced the planned retirement of Chris M. Killian, its Chief Technology and Sustainability Officer. Stephen G. Crawford is set to return in a senior leadership role, overseeing technology projects and sustainability initiatives. See our latest analysis for Eastman Chemical. While leadership changes are underway, Eastman Chemical’s recent insider buying and persistent dividend growth have done little to stem negative momentum. The company’s 1-year total...
